<http://ClimOO/climoo/imports/envo-imports> rdf:type owl:Ontology ;
                                             owl:versionIRI <http://ClimOO/climoo/imports/envo-imports#2025-06-25> ;
                                             rdfs:comment """Additional imports from PATO and ChEBI can be found here.
https://github.com/ClimOO/ClimOO-Ontology/tree/main/ClimOO%20material/src/ontology/imports/pato-imports.ttl
https://github.com/ClimOO/ClimOO-Ontology/tree/main/ClimOO%20material/src/ontology/imports/chebi-imports.ttl"""@en ,
                                                          """This file contains ClimOO Ontology imports from the Environmental Ontology (EnvO). It also contains some imports reused by EnvO from the  Chemical Entities of Biological Interest Ontology (ChEBI), NCBITaxon Ontology (NCBITaxon), the Phenotype And Trait Ontology (PATO), and the Population and Community Ontology (PCO). Imports were manually collected and revised.

Ontology source: http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/envo.owl
Other ontology sources: https://ontobee.org/ontology/CHEBI
https://github.com/obophenotype/ncbitaxon 
https://github.com/PopulationAndCommunityOntology/pco 
https://ontobee.org/ontology/PATO"""@en ;
                                             rdfs:seeAlso "https://github.com/EnvironmentOntology/envo" ;
                                             owl:versionInfo "2025-06-25" .

