   <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Space_weather" ,
                                                            "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Weather"
 ] .


###  http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01001079
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01001079> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                               rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_01001078> ;
                                               <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "Weather which inheres in an atmosphere." ;
