[ rdf:type owl:Axiom ;
   owl:annotatedSource <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02500000> ;
   owl:annotatedProperty rdfs:subClassOf ;
   owl:annotatedTarget _:genid370 ;
   rdfs:comment """ClimOO developer comment:
We omitted the corresponding equivalent class axiom to avoid incorrect automatic reclassifications of “system development” classes. We judged this an adequate compromise as, on one hand, this EnvO class has been created for grouping purposes (see comments to the class), and on the other, the SCO representation of system development requires further implementations.
https://github.com/gioUbbiali/Sustainability-Core-Ontology/issues/2"""@en
 ] .


